metadata.name: TrufflePass #1
metadata.description: Truffle is a tight-knit community of 333 elite traders. Owning a Pass grants lifetime access into our discord and access to our own custom minting bot. Truffle provides cross-chain alpha, futures calls + copy trading, free airdrops for our upcoming projects, daily WL giveaways, & a community of like-minded traders. Our goal at Truffle is to provide quality alpha that can't be found anywhere else.
